rows.label: tlk42100181_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Grampypon of Magomago
always so busy lately!

rows.label: tlk42100181_01_msg0002
rows.name:
In other places, all kinds of people
bring things for selling. But here is
different! Very unhelpful!

rows.label: tlk42100181_01_msg0003
rows.name:
Grampypon not allowed to bring nice
things to sell without get permission
from high-up people. It make no sense!

rows.label: tlk42100181_01_msg0004
rows.name:
Still not nighttime yet? Meh-meh!
Hurry up! Grampypon need his rest!
